        "id": 1002539
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-01-08T23:37:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I asked Nodir and he told me there are buildbucket users that still use \u0027repository\u0027.\n\nThe cost of supporting it in lucicfg is negligible anyway.",
